# Copy this file to `.env` for local testing only. `.env` is gitignored.
#
# When the worker is invoked by a Notion custom agent, it gets a pre-authenticated
# Notion client automatically — you do NOT need to set anything for the deployed worker.
#
# NOTION_API_TOKEN is only used by `ntn workers exec ... --local`, where the runtime
# builds the Notion client from this token.
# NOTION_API_TOKEN=
